dakemoto

How to BN request?
You have to request on "The first week of every month" only
(when I open, you can see it on state of my profile in the middle)

※ This is a form
Aritst - Song : xi - world fragment lll
Link : https://osu.ppy.sh/s/------
Mod applied : Normal(5) Hard(3) Insane(5) Extra(4)
Comment : anything fine. But, sometimes It makes me accept your map by comment. 'w'
Also If your map already bubbled, then you have to write it here.

Please observe the following
※ Please self-mod your map, before request me.
▶make sure the general, patterns, hitsounds, everything.
(carefully do this, If It is not I would say reject you. At least do your best!)
※ The map must not be graveyard(when you request me)
▶It's a proof that you did not self-mod before you request me(so I not add the map in list)
※ no matter what I will reply your message.
▶If I rejected the map, I will say the reason honestly.
※ Honestly, I don't feel like check 4K mapset(but not always '^'*)
▶Sometimes If I really want to feel check the map! then I doing that. I have a right. why not? =w=

Thanks for respect in advance!!
To do list
when I accepted the your request, It will be added here!
There will be a delay of up to two month nearly(maximum)
Depend on the amount of requests that I accepted.
